Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.62,0:01:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅與創造
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.38,0:01:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類何必總是重蹈覆轍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.55,0:01:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很費解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.98,0:01:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類無法直面回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以美化它  誇大它
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:02:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試圖用懷念來包裝疼痛以克服過去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要取回媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.13,0:02:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是出於懷念？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.45,0:02:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了克服眼前的難題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.16,0:02:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指星痕？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實歸根到底是你們的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.32,0:02:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.36,0:02:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你也懼怕回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.86,0:02:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健忘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.76,0:02:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾先生  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快瞧這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中頭彩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.33,0:03:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真噁心啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點不行麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.14,0:03:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷諾  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.36,0:03:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩  快離開...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.49,0:03:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.76,0:03:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊利娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快走...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.43,0:03:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LifeStream
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是巡行在星球的生命之河
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星球和她滋養的  萬物生靈的源頭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神羅公司成功把LifeStream
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:05:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化作了能源
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.21,0:05:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托這個福  我們的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得豐富多彩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這卻是在剝削星球的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反對者也為數不少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.74,0:05:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神羅對反對自己的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動用蠻力去壓制
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神羅麾下有一批特種兵  冠名為「戰士」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很久以前從天而降
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以毀滅星球為己任的災厄——
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑諾娃細胞的移植產物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名叫薩菲羅斯的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很是出類拔萃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.73,0:05:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  他得知了自己誕生於恐怖實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是對神羅懷恨在心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:06:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久而久之  他與一切事物不共戴天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神羅和反對它的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.35,0:06:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩菲羅斯不惜摧毀星球  只因仇深似海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.25,0:06:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多人竭力阻止薩菲羅斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶來了無數戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭與悲劇形影不離
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜愛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.09,0:06:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也化作了LifeStream
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.42,0:06:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於在那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運之日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.01,0:06:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星球用自身的力量平息了一切干戈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星球把LifeStream用作武器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噴出地面的LifeStream
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將紛爭  野望  悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:07:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,統統吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我們用悲傷圓上了句號」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.12,0:07:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這已是兩年前的安慰話了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.19,0:08:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好險
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過星球她...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠比我們想像的要憤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星痕症候群
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  馬琳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.54,0:08:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變什麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:08:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求您
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請留下丹澤爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據調查委今晨頒布的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大氣中的LifeStream濃度僅為2年前的百分之一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經降至對人體毫無影響的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而神羅公司主樓...以及所屬的周邊地區
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.05,0:09:27.60,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡人去樓空哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然屹立於危險濃度中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.57,0:09:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了防患星痕症候群  請遠離存在隱患的設施
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委員會如上警告
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來報道神羅公司被追究的賠償
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.17,0:09:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德  你在哪兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好  是Strife快遞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們服務廣泛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.37,0:10:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然記得你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.89,0:10:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷諾從圓球別墅來電話了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要委託你工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德  你還好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信息完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.63,0:11:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說卡達裘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:11:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是哥哥的鎮？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.52,0:12:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們受歡迎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對夠嗆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別掉淚啊  亞祖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽和他在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.94,0:12:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可難說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別哭啊  羅茲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.13,0:12:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧啊  說曹操曹操到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥給藏起來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你玩弄了我？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽果然在你們手裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別吼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.63,0:13:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懶得和你說了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換社長接
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.03,0:15:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是逃避了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  我是巴雷特 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.69,0:15:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子成功了  找到新油田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.98,0:15:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,油~田~  超級大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在有眉目了  不久就去見馬琳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我轉達一下  掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.57,0:15:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷諾又來電話了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.80,0:15:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,催你盡快去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.27,0:15:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺有點怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己當心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.50,0:16:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然有兩下子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯德  大帥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不一般
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自封的原士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.62,0:16:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身手依舊不凡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.01,0:16:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是路法斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.91,0:16:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真背運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天我...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.90,0:16:55.86,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我何干
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大樓坍塌前  勉強...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.36,0:16:58.37,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰襲擊的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.38,0:16:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逼我走人麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫個忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.99,0:17:06.48,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們神羅公司欠世界一筆大債
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害得世界慘淡而寥落
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.02,0:17:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們把責任推給我們也合乎情理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是這筆債非還不可
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:22.66,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開個門
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為第一步棋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.44,0:17:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們調查起薩菲羅斯遺留的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.24,0:17:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去兩年了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.08,0:17:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界邁出了復興的一步  什麼構成了最大威脅？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  是萬惡的星痕症候群
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們認為原因出在薩菲羅斯身上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.92,0:17:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世人認為魔晃爐  魔晃能源
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.70,0:17:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及LifeStream是星痕的原因正在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:18:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看未必
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LifeStream與星球一起誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔晃能源更有40多年的利用史
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.70,0:18:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星痕在歷史上從未有過登場
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.68,0:18:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我們這一代和有不同尋常？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不出別的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是薩菲羅斯的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩菲羅斯死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的精神去了哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溶解在了LifeStream中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倘若它未擴散而巡行在星球  那會怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.23,0:18:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  這終究是我的遐想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.02,0:18:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻不無可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知曉真相才會推動星痕的治癒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.03,0:18:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我們...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調查了薩菲羅斯留下的蛛絲馬跡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:18:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可曾記得？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.07,0:19:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北方大空洞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你猜有何收穫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.43,0:19:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那兒一無所獲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過卻節外生枝了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們出現了...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快...快走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡達裘一夥兒人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡達裘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他連你也不會放過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.63,0:19:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你與他們有過交手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是局外人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.21,0:19:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲早會物歸原主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:47.59,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.98,0:19:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你與我們一樣  與薩菲羅斯有很深的過往
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.03,0:19:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果卡達裘的目的是給來臨的那一刻做鋪墊...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:20:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們無疑是最大的障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋪墊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩菲羅斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捲土重來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.45,0:20:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說完了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼切入正題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.36,0:20:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了與卡達裘他們抗衡  我們需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何不並肩作戰？原士兵·克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.38,0:20:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自封的罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.84,0:20:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽是指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.47,0:20:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡達裘他們掛在嘴上的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.01,0:20:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路法斯  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你隱瞞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你我站在同一戰線  我怎麼會隱瞞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於星痕的情報想必你也需要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.88,0:20:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了生活在同一屋簷下的孤兒們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.89,0:21:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓孩子們再次綻放笑顏如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的最終目的是重建世界  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.63,0:21:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託啦  克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.62,0:21:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓神羅公司東山再起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這個雅興
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.67,0:21:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷諾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.35,0:21:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德住在這兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.12,0:21:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.36,0:22:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.82,0:22:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和丹澤爾一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.40,0:22:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德也生病了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.44,0:22:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說一聲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.12,0:22:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為病了  才出走的？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.97,0:22:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要獨自去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.14,0:22:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.24,0:22:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.88,0:22:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他根本沒有鬥志
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.49,0:22:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂法？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.75,0:22:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回去吧  馬琳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.42,0:22:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  我要見克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.27,0:23:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.85,0:23:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多想見見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.87,0:23:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見面之後怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.84,0:23:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拽他回家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.78,0:23:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過...說教在先
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.55,0:23:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.74,0:23:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來要找主任和伊利娜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他社員提供的情報呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.27,0:23:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時沒有收穫...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.98,0:23:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來的社員  來齊了這麼多真是超出預料
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.64,0:23:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我淚流滿面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.39,0:23:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看能重新來過
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.54,0:23:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贖罪的重任  落在活下來的人身上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.80,0:23:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去兩年了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.43,0:23:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.76,0:23:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才兩年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.02,0:24:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那簡直是噩夢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.34,0:24:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界險些滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.10,0:24:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們神羅惹的禍
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.02,0:24:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說真的  我們要贖多少罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.37,0:24:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少了主任果然很頭疼啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.93,0:24:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊利娜也是  千萬給我活的好好的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.22,0:24:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.81,0:24:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾先生和社長一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.33,0:24:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九死一生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.82,0:24:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運氣好的很
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.71,0:24:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.90,0:24:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.88,0:24:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教堂？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.88,0:25:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  那個地方的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.97,0:25:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.44,0:26:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七號街的電話均無法接通
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.32,0:26:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七號街的電話均無法接通
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.50,0:26:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七號街的電話均無法接通
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.60,0:26:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七號街的電話均無法接通
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.83,0:27:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七號街的電話均無法接通
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.96,0:27:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.93,0:27:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接到你的電話真是太陽打西邊出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.39,0:27:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.92,0:27:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.06,0:27:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.48,0:27:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰？這是克勞德的電話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.42,0:27:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.38,0:27:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.33,0:27:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.02,0:28:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道怎麼辦好
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.06,0:28:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哭嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.22,0:28:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  你沒事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.22,0:28:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德  克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.04,0:28:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.83,0:28:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.89,0:28:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.73,0:29:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最煩說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.91,0:29:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.44,0:29:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我如實交代
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.54,0:29:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那東西在逃離你們的途中從飛機不慎掉落
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.96,0:29:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太失態了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.96,0:29:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當真麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.60,0:29:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.72,0:29:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妨向這個發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.27,0:29:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的何在
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.83,0:29:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽的力量是必需的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.08,0:29:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了再聚合絕不能少
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.08,0:29:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(593,645)\fs45}Reunion
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.04,0:29:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再聚合
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.84,0:30:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲得母親細胞的同伴齊聚一堂
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.63,0:30:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後報復星球
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.64,0:30:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備工作穩步進行著
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.88,0:30:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞧  都怪某些人把媽媽藏了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.69,0:30:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.50,0:30:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星痕
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.48,0:30:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長也頗有體會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.68,0:30:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這多虧在LifeStream中
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.61,0:30:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有媽媽的遺傳意念在掙扎著
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.33,0:30:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再看看我們
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.19,0:30:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然不清楚媽媽在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.03,0:30:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丟死人了  但卻無可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.93,0:30:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰讓我們是區區意念體
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.72,0:30:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有找到媽媽後分得細胞
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.94,0:30:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能夠復原
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.57,0:30:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光有意念和星痕遠談不上準備充分
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.82,0:30:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了完美的再聚合
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.08,0:30:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼亂糟糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.22,0:31:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長  您有所預感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.74,0:31:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.48,0:31:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  星痕
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.76,0:31:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別出門嚇唬人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.11,0:32:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.73,0:32:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍在人在
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.61,0:32:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然下過決心...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.17,0:32:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想成為戰士啊  加把勁
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.17,0:32:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  感覺如何
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.24,0:32:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  到達米德加爾後
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.60,0:32:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼打算
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.73,0:32:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.02,0:33:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔  找個岩石在後面停車
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.47,0:33:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德  我們下車
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.60,0:33:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的榮耀和夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.78,0:33:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.21,0:33:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.55,0:33:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見證了我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.65,0:33:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發誓過永不忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.29,0:33:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.23,0:33:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.82,0:33:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別假裝悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.49,0:33:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也無需演繹義憤填膺
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.14,0:33:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為克勞德...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.75,0:33:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.79,0:33:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.03,0:34:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來玩玩？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.21,0:34:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  不願意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.56,0:34:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.45,0:34:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難聞
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.76,0:34:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  媽媽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.32,0:34:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兒沒有別人了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.42,0:34:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  來玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.86,0:35:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人沸騰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.82,0:36:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂法
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.62,0:36:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找錯地方了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.20,0:37:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒哭
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.70,0:37:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  我帶她去
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.74,0:37:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.61,0:38:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.74,0:38:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.06,0:38:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.42,0:38:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.91,0:38:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.15,0:38:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.68,0:38:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.64,0:38:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.10,0:38:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也得了星痕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.23,0:39:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人能治好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.90,0:39:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂法
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.48,0:39:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂法
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.71,0:40:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.25,0:40:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.83,0:40:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不認識他
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.30,0:40:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬琳
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.37,0:40:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混賬
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.61,0:41:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉死我了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.44,0:41:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老兄  你跟孩子們生活的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.32,0:41:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.06,0:41:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袖手旁觀？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.86,0:41:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.74,0:42:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽快些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.77,0:42:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂法要我帶你過去
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.02,0:42:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊咯
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.48,0:43:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會治好我們？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.77,0:43:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.82,0:43:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  管他是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.24,0:43:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是哥哥藏的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.94,0:43:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從LifeStream中誕生的新力量
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.22,0:43:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓魔石球賜給我們新能力
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.79,0:43:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是母親留給我們的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.44,0:43:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.94,0:44:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽也被哥哥藏起來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.89,0:44:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是那個社長
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.02,0:44:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神羅公司一向喜歡把媽媽藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.69,0:44:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不妨把神羅的相關建築搜個遍
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.24,0:44:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  更多夥伴會蜂擁而至
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.87,0:44:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.30,0:44:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過先要...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.90,0:44:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向哥哥發發牢騷
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.95,0:44:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝作自己是局外人
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.97,0:44:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.10,0:44:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.28,0:45:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷諾他們在四處打聽
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.65,0:45:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星痕症候群  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.87,0:45:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了也無所謂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.32,0:45:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.37,0:45:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有治癒的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.55,0:45:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  丹澤爾卻從來不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.00,0:45:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起面對它不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.43,0:45:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相幫助  一起奮鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.73,0:45:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是真正的家人  果然不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.13,0:45:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能...  誰也救不了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.30,0:45:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人也好  同伴也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.33,0:45:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都救不了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.85,0:46:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖拖拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.61,0:46:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖拖拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.53,0:46:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拖到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.69,0:46:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還找不到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.47,0:46:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有目擊者稱  是被那幫傢伙帶走的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.94,0:46:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.09,0:46:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘卻之都
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.16,0:46:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們老家
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.12,0:46:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親眷顧我一份特殊力量
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.04,0:46:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能與折磨人的罪魁——星球作戰的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.77,0:46:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實你們也有這個能力
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.42,0:47:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.90,0:47:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.34,0:47:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼承了溶解在LifeStream中  母親遺傳意念的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.35,0:47:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被選中的一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.91,0:47:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.80,0:47:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星球在百般阻撓
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.60,0:47:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它試圖停止我們成長
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.81,0:47:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說  你們遭受皮肉之苦  痛不欲生
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.64,0:47:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你們治好
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.52,0:47:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後回到母親身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.35,0:47:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一家人齊心協力  報復星球
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.74,0:47:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟著我做
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.56,0:48:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹澤爾
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.18,0:48:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹澤爾
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.42,0:48:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親  您瞧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.85,0:49:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多了這麼多兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.39,0:49:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到與母親見面
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.85,0:49:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不會寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.21,0:49:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.93,0:49:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都要垮掉了  還來
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.31,0:49:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一定是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.98,0:49:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提問一下
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.21,0:50:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.31,0:50:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.83,0:50:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想獲得原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.25,0:50:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我想被原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.57,0:50:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.04,0:51:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然來了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.62,0:51:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來領孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.05,0:51:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼前這位
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.82,0:51:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.89,0:51:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過呢  
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.70,0:51:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺憾的是
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.28,0:51:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.75,0:51:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.70,0:53:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是救不了任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.47,0:53:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文森特  怎樣一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.25,0:53:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我常來此地
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.63,0:54:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因而卡達裘們的一舉一動我全看在眼裡
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.85,0:54:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂星痕...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.83,0:54:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是排除體內異物的系統反應過剩所致
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.61,0:54:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體內也有類似LifeStraem的循環
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.57,0:54:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它與入侵的邪惡物質對峙
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.22,0:54:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪惡物質
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.65,0:54:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩菲羅斯因子  傑諾娃的遺傳意念
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.95,0:54:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你怎麼稱呼
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.43,0:54:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好詳細
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.58,0:54:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾和伊利娜  
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.59,0:54:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奄奄一息著被搬到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.00,0:54:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必是被严加拷問的後果
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.48,0:54:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救倒是救了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.80,0:54:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生死難說
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.23,0:54:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拷問？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.17,0:54:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.66,0:54:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們入手了傑諾娃的頭
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.75,0:54:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡達裘所找的母親是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.89,0:55:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上天遣送的凶神惡煞——
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.19,0:55:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑諾娃
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.67,0:55:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用她造出第二個薩菲羅斯也不無可能
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.52,0:55:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡達裘...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.62,0:55:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.34,0:55:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想琢磨
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.90,0:55:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬琳
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.74,0:55:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.64,0:55:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹澤爾和蒂法她...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.48,0:55:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂法沒有事
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.71,0:55:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟蒂法說話
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.19,0:55:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有手機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.18,0:55:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼天啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.95,0:55:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文森特  幫我把馬琳送到店裡
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.69,0:55:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去聽聽神羅有什麼高見
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.73,0:55:51.86,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是上策
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.86,0:55:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.56,0:55:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.95,0:55:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼總是一意孤行
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.77,0:56:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬琳
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.45,0:56:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再忍耐一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.22,0:56:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥就要打響
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.47,0:56:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  光靠刀槍不能解決問題
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.85,0:56:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.82,0:56:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.18,0:56:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德  這關乎戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.53,0:56:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.93,0:56:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘卻之都
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.69,0:56:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們老家
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.56,0:56:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.47,0:56:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去和路法斯談談
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.25,0:56:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.44,0:56:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.53,0:56:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了孩子們可能也無能為力
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.30,0:56:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次釀出無法挽回的事也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.89,0:56:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你害怕這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.29,0:56:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  請你面對複雜的現實吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.12,0:56:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負擔重？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.04,0:56:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重是應該的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.08,0:56:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學不會一個人生活就要學會忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.71,0:56:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明耐不住寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.27,0:56:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不接  手機卻從不離身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.74,0:57:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們老家  你還不快去
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.89,0:57:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道我們...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.91,0:57:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸給回憶不成
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.42,0:57:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我曾經見死不救啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.05,0:57:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拖拖拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.77,0:57:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  快放過可憐的自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.23,0:57:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪能被原諒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.90,0:57:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不曾嘗試
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.58,0:57:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘗試？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.60,0:57:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘗試
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.82,0:57:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬琳  我們回去
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.81,0:57:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來嘗試一番
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.19,0:58:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果會聯繫給你
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.36,0:58:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是李富
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.04,0:58:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作順暢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.32,0:58:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了下傳單  好一個不賺錢的生意
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.72,0:58:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻也是克勞德先生的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.49,0:58:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很樂意盡一份綿薄之力  日後聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.06,0:58:36.98,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.35,0:58:38.68,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有工作委託你  好久不見  我是尤菲醬
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.91,0:58:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五台的孩子們失蹤一事你清楚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.77,0:58:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我點消息哈  拜託咯
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.84,0:58:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級大  我有眉目了  過一段就去見馬琳  幫我轉達一下  掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.75,0:58:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己當心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.91,0:58:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從來都沒怨過你的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.25,0:58:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.04,0:58:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.74,0:59:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們聾了？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.32,0:59:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  裝聽不見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.87,0:59:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做這種事要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.85,0:59:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對孩子做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.71,0:59:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有希
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.12,1:00:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹澤爾
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.59,1:00:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹澤爾
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.92,1:00:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹澤爾
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.94,1:01:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.25,1:01:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽就在這兒吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.73,1:01:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說說思路
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.05,1:01:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個叫什麼呢...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.77,1:01:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀念碑  是神羅造的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.41,1:01:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說藏在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.63,1:01:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.09,1:01:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.33,1:01:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒被告訴
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.89,1:01:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞧  果然是藏在某地
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.85,1:01:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯德  你來頂一句
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.67,1:02:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.78,1:02:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.21,1:02:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒有丹澤爾那麼疼
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.20,1:02:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能治好嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.17,1:02:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.01,1:02:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為了丹澤爾找遍了各種方法呢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.22,1:02:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.03,1:02:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰讓你從來不收拾桌子
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.18,1:02:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.69,1:02:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德是因為丹澤爾的星痕治不好  所以離家出走的？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.90,1:02:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是因為自己也有了星痕
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.19,1:02:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.32,1:02:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連自己都照顧不過來
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.25,1:02:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一想就...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.66,1:03:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己都照顧不過來  還提什麼保護家人！
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.53,1:03:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老爹說的
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.32,1:03:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德你別放棄
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.85,1:03:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬琳  丹澤爾  蒂法
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.25,1:03:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是在幫助我呢
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.66,1:03:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總是被人保護著
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.94,1:03:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回要輪到我了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.30,1:03:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.61,1:03:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  卡達裘
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.61,1:03:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問你一件事
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.56,1:03:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此一件哦
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.33,1:03:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過  要用傑諾娃細胞來復原
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.93,1:03:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該怎麼理解？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.18,1:03:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他...會回來
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.87,1:04:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩菲羅斯  
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.07,1:04:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噩夢啊
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.48,1:04:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.88,1:04:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.13,1:04:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟薩菲羅斯沒有瓜葛
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.56,1:04:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是對他有感覺
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.07,1:04:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人心煩
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.86,1:04:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽青睞我和薩菲羅斯哪一個呢...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.81,1:04:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意念體真是可憐
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.25,1:04:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你們的下場只有一個
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.43,1:04:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽長途跋涉來到這個星球
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.47,1:04:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓愚蠢的傢伙們灰飛煙滅
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.71,1:04:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你清楚
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.71,1:04:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡和媽媽來的時候相比絲毫沒改善
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.27,1:04:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來博得母親歡心
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.28,1:04:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對母親...唯命是從
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.76,1:04:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  噩夢再臨是嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.96,1:05:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們一日不消失  就會重蹈覆轍
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.42,1:05:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星球上循環往復的LifeStream
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.52,1:05:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在生死之間徘徊而無阻
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.53,1:05:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果生命的原貌就是這般週而復始
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.98,1:05:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那歷史的重演也就是必然事件
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.41,1:05:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑諾娃也好薩菲羅斯也罷
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.64,1:05:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管去惹是生非好了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.00,1:05:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會遵循生命的安排
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.18,1:05:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不厭其煩地挫敗你們
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.09,1:05:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長  這是給搶走媽媽找托辭？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.92,1:05:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際卻暗自後悔吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.58,1:05:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後悔？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.71,1:05:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我樂此不疲
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.32,1:05:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再好不過
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.97,1:06:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  也該落幕了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.38,1:07:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹澤爾  我們得離開了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.73,1:07:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.76,1:07:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難度太大
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.49,1:08:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它來沒？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.19,1:08:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒膽量看
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.96,1:09:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樂趣無窮啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.79,1:09:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊透頂啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.95,1:09:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們有完沒完
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.55,1:09:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實把母親奉還就一了百了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.46,1:09:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們拿傑諾娃的頭做什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.36,1:09:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼再聚合  吃錯藥啦？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.31,1:10:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只想見見母親
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.47,1:10:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親會決定今後的所有事
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.94,1:10:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  母親在哪
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.27,1:10:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親來母親去的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.00,1:10:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是傑諾娃的項上人頭麼
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.88,1:10:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.70,1:10:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許這麼稱呼母親
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.06,1:10:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒不了你
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.26,1:10:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我錯了  
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.58,1:10:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.52,1:10:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道什麼鳥歉啊
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.87,1:11:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂法？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.01,1:11:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王八蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.93,1:11:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這兒保護你媽
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.76,1:11:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴雷特
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.34,1:12:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬琳還好好的吧  啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.23,1:12:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不過啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.22,1:12:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我暈...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.58,1:12:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰動了我的磨石球
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.70,1:12:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用問  來者不善
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.51,1:12:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臥槽~
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.90,1:12:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.73,1:13:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型的  希艾拉號
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.56,1:13:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒讓你們坐坐
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.08,1:13:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買電話怎麼走
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.53,1:13:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.69,1:13:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是夥伴
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.20,1:13:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹澤爾  能一個人跑回店裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.74,1:13:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.38,1:13:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有完沒完
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.13,1:13:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂法
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.35,1:14:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹澤爾
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.91,1:14:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.51,1:14:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.31,1:14:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.61,1:14:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.50,1:14:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.91,1:14:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬琳平安  我把她留在了店裡
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.28,1:14:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.06,1:14:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕鬆了不少
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.77,1:15:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總拖來拖去  拖輕了包袱
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.09,1:15:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人回店裡吧  
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.85,1:15:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟馬琳等你們
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.23,1:15:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德也會回家吧
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.78,1:15:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.86,1:16:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會輸給你啊
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.78,1:18:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早點登場啊
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.26,1:19:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有意思啊  社長
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.44,1:19:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來召喚什麼好
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.96,1:19:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.81,1:19:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都沒發現  不孝順
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.53,1:19:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宰了它  克勞德
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.80,1:19:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.96,1:20:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.56,1:20:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還早著呢
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.59,1:21:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.37,1:22:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.22,1:22:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.54,1:22:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.21,1:24:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打架不要找錯人啊
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.98,1:25:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯德
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.06,1:25:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好不好大事不好
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.51,1:25:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  魯德  你沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.46,1:25:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實很有事...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.78,1:26:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩~
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.78,1:28:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿  搭檔
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.86,1:28:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.31,1:28:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很強大嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.83,1:28:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凝聚了神羅的科技與汗水
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.41,1:28:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你研發的麼
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.02,1:28:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威力姑且不說  華麗得很
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.94,1:28:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.10,1:28:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡吧  搭檔
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.21,1:28:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可以告別加班咯
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.99,1:30:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.63,1:30:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.29,1:30:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.89,1:32:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走  克勞德
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.89,1:32:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好不容易見到了媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.08,1:32:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來做什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.48,1:32:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親自有安排
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.60,1:32:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意念體一無所知麼
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.35,1:32:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我是傀儡
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.66,1:33:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和過去的你...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.34,1:33:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無二致
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.40,1:33:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德  磨石球在此
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.10,1:33:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別搖晃啊
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.65,1:33:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希德  快降落
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.33,1:33:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  自己不會跳啊  跳
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.23,1:33:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別插手
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.04,1:33:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.54,1:33:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是薩菲羅斯的意念體
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.64,1:33:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好比是幼蟲
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.85,1:33:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼蟲
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.86,1:33:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲子  他是蟲子啊
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.28,1:33:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘  安靜點
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.71,1:33:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晚變身成薩菲羅斯麼
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.45,1:34:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說  克勞德知道這事嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.53,1:34:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕知情
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.21,1:34:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.88,1:34:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我們不插手
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.58,1:34:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理解不能  快說明下
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.56,1:34:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人的話題
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.93,1:34:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性別歧視  大男子主義
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.92,1:34:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘  閉上嘴
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.95,1:34:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺們兒也蒙在鼓裡
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.08,1:34:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2年前
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.87,1:34:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終決戰的時候明明有過的鬥志
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.31,1:34:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻被短短的兩年時間沖淡了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.61,1:34:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想克勞德又點燃了鬥志
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.86,1:34:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  我忍他10分鐘
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.47,1:34:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德事兒真多
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.89,1:34:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這叫坦率
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.22,1:36:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的再結合
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.45,1:36:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你見識一番
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.34,1:36:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久違了啊  克勞德
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.65,1:36:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消了星痕啊
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.70,1:36:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不勝惋惜
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.43,1:36:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的何在
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.40,1:36:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死在星痕之下的亡魂
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.05,1:36:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴著LifeStream巡行在這個星球
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.99,1:37:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晚侵蝕星球
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.46,1:37:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德  我的願望是
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.91,1:37:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以星球作舟  向宇宙的黑暗啟航
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.51,1:37:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如當年的母親
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.57,1:37:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們早晚會物色好另一顆星球
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.05,1:37:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡創造繁花似錦的未來
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.42,1:37:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的星球會怎樣
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.37,1:37:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道  看你本事了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.77,1:37:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.57,1:38:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？  什麼使你變強了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.18,1:38:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懶得和你說
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.20,1:39:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在物色送你的見面禮
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.84,1:39:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送你「絕望」如何？
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.15,1:39:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跪地求饒給我看
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.28,1:41:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當年的疼痛你可曾記得  克勞德
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.67,1:41:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻再次  賜予你刻骨銘心的痛
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.15,1:42:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你而言什麼最重要？
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.44,1:42:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我奪來快樂一下如何
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.17,1:42:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換做是我  絕對不放棄
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.57,1:42:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便情形很絕望
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.67,1:42:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,握緊你的夢想
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.59,1:42:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時刻與戰士的榮耀同在
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.44,1:42:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  雖沒成為戰士  也不妨抱著那顆心
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.47,1:42:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎克斯
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.46,1:42:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我幫你一把？
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.24,1:43:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的手下敗將而已  輕鬆搞定他
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.88,1:43:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.54,1:43:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再忘了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.63,1:43:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你生命的見證
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.94,1:43:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可悲啊  你一無所知
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.31,1:43:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都很珍貴
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.96,1:44:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在回憶中安息吧
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.70,1:44:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.11,1:44:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會成為回憶
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.14,1:45:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.90,1:45:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡達裘
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.46,1:45:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.82,1:45:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也該放棄努力了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.37,1:45:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是媽媽...嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.34,1:45:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回大家身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.51,1:45:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.51,1:47:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  知道厲害了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.81,1:47:03.87,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.02,1:47:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純爺們兒~  克勞德是純爺們兒~
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.46,1:47:08.04,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德想做就能成功
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.76,1:47:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個抓穩了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.93,1:47:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都守候在我們身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.63,1:47:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.81,1:47:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.65,1:48:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.79,1:48:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起玩
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.78,1:48:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.08,1:48:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德也會回家吧
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.26,1:49:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.25,1:49:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.22,1:50:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.10,1:50:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還這麼叫
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.47,1:50:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三番五次叫我媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:50:53.09,1:50:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不好  多親切
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.74,1:50:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼大的孩子要不起
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.89,1:51:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾  你不屬於這兒
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.52,1:52:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐說克勞德會來這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.76,1:52:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,1:52:21.89,1:52:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:26.77,1:52:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一些孩子還留有星痕
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.31,1:52:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:52:38.49,1:52:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧  讓他幫你治好
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.44,1:52:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以放心了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.94,1:52:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.71,1:53:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬歲
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.01,1:53:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都給我跳進去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,1:53:44.22,1:53:45.61,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治好了治好了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:33.49,1:54:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後  沒問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:54:58.41,1:54:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:55:01.52,1:55:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:04.85,1:55:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,2000)}並不孤單
